此高架車站在1917年2月1日啟用<ref name=AstoriaExtension>{{cite web|title=First Train Runs On Elevated Line to Astoria Section|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/54438288/?terms=ditmars+boulevard+subway+station|via=[[Newspapers.com|Newspapers.com]]|publisher=[[Brooklyn_Daily_Eagle|Brooklyn Daily Eagle]]|accessdate=2015-06-29|date=1917-02-01|archive-date=2019-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905063043/https://www.newspapers.com/image/54438288/?terms=ditmars+boulevard+subway+station|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此站設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]和三條軌道。中央軌道不營運，但2002年前曾有定期列車行駛<ref>{{Cite web|title = www.nycsubway.org: BMT Astoria Line|url = http://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/BMT_Astoria_Line|website = www.nycsubway.org|access-date = 2016-02-19|archive-date = 2020-11-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201130041204/https://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/BMT_Astoria_Line|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title = 30 Avenue-Grand Avenue (N,Q) - The SubwayNut|url = http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/30n/index.php|website = www.subwaynut.com|access-date = 2016-02-19|first = Jeremiah|last = Cox|archive-date = 2020-07-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200706134819/http://subwaynut.com/bmt/30n/index.php|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

月台南端較狹窄。月台兩端包括全高的網狀屏風，而月台中央部分則有玻璃屏風和黑色金屬雨棚。2018年翻新前，兩個月台全部設有奶油色屏風，月台中央則設紅色木造雨棚<ref name=":0"/>。

2018年此站的車站藝術《Perasma I and II; Dappleganger》由{{link-en|斯提芬·威斯霍爾|Stephen Westfall}}，由夾層的薄膜玻璃面板組成<ref>{{cite web | title=Astoria subway stations reopen after 8-month redesign | website=am New York | date=2018-06-22 | url=https://www.amny.com/transit/astoria-subway-stations-1.19356502 | access-date=2018-06-25 | archive-date=2020-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924065427/https://www.amny.com/transit/astoria-subway-stations-1.19356502/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 出口 ===
此站唯一的夾層是月台中央和軌道下方的高架木造車站大堂。各月台設有一系列閘機和兩條樓梯。北側詢問處後設有下通道。兩側月台樓梯後方通道可下降至31街和30大道交界的東南角或西南角。另一側的兩條樓梯則往西北角或東北角<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web |title=N Train |url=http://www.stationreporter.net/ntrain.htm |date=2012-02-04 |access-date=2016-02-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204051427/http://www.stationreporter.net/ntrain.htm |archivedate=2012-02-04 }}</ref><ref name=maps>{{cite web|title=MTA Neighborhood Maps: Astoria|url=http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/qns/Q1_Astoria_2015.pdf|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=2015-09-27|date=2015|archive-date=2018-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123153318/http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/qns/Q1_Astoria_2015.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。北行月台只限出口樓梯下降至新城大道和31街交界東南角。

